title: Ep. - 454 - HOW TO WIN THE BACHELOR WITH GAME OF ROSES GAMING WALL STREET
description:
Chad Kultgen and Lizzie Pace, co-hosts of the Game of Roses podcast , and authors of How to Win The Bachelor: The Secret to Finding Love and Fame on America's Favorite Reality Show.

 

Tobias Deml and Tessa Byford, Director and Producer of Gaming Wall Street. Narrated by Kieran, this two-part documentary explores the historic 2021 short squeeze of GameStop, and how a group of armchair investors and online vigilantes ultimately helped expose the dark underbelly of Wall Street.

 

 

Reality Life with Kate Casey
